        "# Glossary {.unnumbered .appendix #glos}\n",
        "\n",
        "::: {.column-page-right #gloslist}\n",
        "- [a](#arcbeat){#ab}: arcbeat, a hundred thousandth of a circle, 0.0036 degrees, .216 arcminutes, 12.96 arcseconds\n",
        "- [b](#beat){#b}: beat, centimilliday, a hundred thousandth of an day, 864 milliseconds\n",
        "    - [mb](#millibeat){#mb}: millibeat, centimicroday, a thousandth of a beat, a hundred millionth of a day, 864 microseconds\n",
        "- [bpc](#beatpercentiday){#bpc}: a musical or heart beat per centiday, a tenth of a beat per milliday, 0.069[4]{.vinculum} beats per minute, 100 beats per day\n",
        "- [bpm](#beatpermilliday){#bpm}: a musical or heart beat per milliday, ten beats per centiday, 0.69[4]{.vinculum} beats per minute, 1000 beats per day\n",
        "- [bmi](#bodymassindex){#bmi}: body mass index, kilograins of body mass divided by height in zem squared (kg/z&sup2;)\n",
        "- [c](#taur){#c}: taur, 𝜏*r*, 100000 kilozem, 40000 kilometers, nearly the circumference of the Earth, roughly the product of 𝜏 and the radius of the Earth, approximately the dividend of the surface area and the diameter of the Earth\n",
        "    - [mc](#millitaur){#mc}: millitaur, *m*𝜏*r*, a thousandth of a taur, 100 kilozem, 40 kilometers\n",
        "    - [nc](#nanotaur){#nc}: nanotaur, *n*𝜏*r*, a thousandth of a taur, 100 millizem, 1 decizem, 4 centimeters\n",
        "    - [nc&sup3;](#cubicnanotaur){#nc3}: cubic nanotaur, *n*𝜏*r*&sup3;, 1 cubic decizem\n",
        "- [d](#day){#d}: day, a tenth of a decaday, a seventh of week, a fifth of a pentaday, 10 decidays, 24 hours, 100 centidays, 1000 millidays, 1440 minutes, 86400 seconds, 100000 beats, the inverse of a quotidie\n",
        "    - [dek](#decaday){#dek}: decaday, a group of ten days, 2 pentadays\n",
        "    - [pent](#pentaday){#pent}: pentaday, a group of five days, half a decaday\n",
        "    - [dod](#dayofdek){#dod}: day of decaday\n",
        "        - [ba](#dod0){#d0}: the name of day of decaday 0, the frontmost voiced consonant and the most open vowel \n",
        "        - [ve](#dod1){#d1}: the name of day of decaday 1, the second frontmost voiced consonant and the second most open vowel \n",
        "        - [di](#dod2){#d2}: the name of day of decaday 2, the third frontmost voiced consonant and the third most open vowel \n",
        "        - [zo](#dod3){#d3}: the name of day of decaday 3, the fourth frontmost voiced consonant and the fourth most open vowel \n",
        "        - [gu](#dod4){#d4}: the name of day of decaday 4, the least frontmost voiced consonant and the least open vowel\n",
        "        - [pa](#dod5){#d5}: the name of day of decaday 5, the frontmost voiceless consonant and the most open vowel\n",
        "        - [fe](#dod6){#d6}: the name of day of decaday 6, the second frontmost voiceless consonant and the second most open vowel\n",
        "        - [ti](#dod7){#d7}: the name of day of decaday 7, the third frontmost voiceless consonant and the third most open vowel\n",
        "        - [so](#dod8){#d8}: the name of day of decaday 8, the fourth frontmost voiceless consonant and the fourth most open vowel\n",
        "        - [ku](#dod9){#d9}: the name of day of decaday 9, the least frontmost voiceless consonant and the least open vowel\n",
        "    - [dop](#dayofpent){#dop}: day of pentaday\n",
        "    - [dom](#dayofmonth){#dom}: day of month\n",
        "    - [dow](#dayofweek){#dow}: day of week\n",
        "    - [doy](#dayofyear){#doy}: day of year, decaday * 10 + dod\n",
        "    - [dd](#deciday){#dd}: deciday, a tenth of a day, 2.4 hours, 144 minutes\n",
